race.comment: READY TO SCHIPP (15) has put back-to-back wins together including saluting over this track and trip last time out. Hard to knock mares in form and she can bring up the hat-trick against this line-up. ALECTRONA (16) is on the doorstep of another victory with five consecutive runner-up finishes. Gets in well at the weights with the claim and should be right there at the business end. COSMO CENTAURUS (9) has been in the mix in all three outings this campaign and winning rider Moor stays on top. Include in calculations. CHIEF WITNESS (8) best of the rest on the back of a last-start win at Eagle Farm.
